window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Haunted. Despised. Feared.</b></p> <p>The Supernaturals are destroying humanity. <br> <br> Meet Tristan Montague. Leader of the elite group of mages known as the Ordarum. The war against the Supernaturals has raged for years, and humanity is losing. <br> <br> When the Ordarum is given a suicide mission to recover an artifact that can end the war and hand victory to humanity - Tristan takes it, knowing it may be his last. </p> <p>Now, together with his squad, they must face an unspeakable enemy, overwhelming odds, and secure an ultimate weapon - or die trying. </p>"; 
